---
title: Rich Lamb Ragu with Basil Ricotta Clouds
description: Set the table first becasue this lamb ragout will be done in less than 25 mins! Ritch lamb ragout, aldente rigagtoni, dolloped with savoury clouds of ricotta, parmesan and basil.
